author: Marisa Schultz
title: Trump on origins of coronavirus in Chinese lab: "We're going to find out"
description: President Trump said Friday the federal government is investigating whether the origin of the coronavirus originated in a Wuhan lab and the U.S. government will find out how the deadly pandemic was unleashed from China.
content:
President Trump said Friday the federal government is investigating whether the novel coronavirus originated in a Wuhan lab and pledged the U.S. government will find out how the deadly pandemic was unleashed from China.
